OL,6,GOfcom is expected to say soon whether
OL,7,Git will run a full consultation on
OL,8,Gchanges to the TV advertising rules.
OL,10,FIt sought views over the summer on
OL,11,Fwhether there was a case to change the
OL,12,Fextra rules covering ITV, Channel 4 and
OL,13,FChannel 5.
OL,15,FThe three PSBs have less advertising in
OL,16,Ftotal than other commercial channels
OL,17,Fand rules on the frequency of breaks
OL,18,Fare tighter.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G1/6
