OL,6,FBut if you imagine there was some
OL,7,Fbenefit to viewers in this, think
OL,8,Fagain.
OL,10,FInstead, the network news followed its
OL,11,Fusual format but the ad breaks were
OL,12,Freplaced by what I call the Trailer
OL,13,FBreaks of Doom.
OL,15,FThese are the full-length breaks
OL,16,Fdesigned for commercials which are
OL,17,Ffilled entirely by promotions because
OL,18,Fof the rules on the volume of
OL,19,Fadvertising on PSBs.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G4/6
