OL,6,FBut, as I've argued before, it is hard
OL,7,Fto claim that viewers will lose out if
OL,8,FITV and others have a full 12 minutes
OL,9,Fof ads all through the most popular
OL,10,Fviewing hours.
OL,12,FPromo breaks are, if anything, more
OL,13,Ffrustrating for viewers but do not pay
OL,14,Ffor the content.
OL,3,COfcom decision on TV advertising rules
OL,4,Cconsultation due soon
